# Implementation Plan - Vevox Parser & Kanban UI

This plan outlines the steps to build a modern Kanban-style UI for visualizing and categorizing Vevox Q&A data with Gemini AI integration.

## Proposed Tech Stack
- Frontend: React (Vite)
- Styling: Tailwind CSS
- Drag & Drop: @hello-pangea/dnd
- AI Integration: Google Generative AI SDK
- Persistence: LocalStorage

