## How to Run

1.  **Parser**: Run `node index.js <VEVOX_URL>` to fetch new data. It will save to `frontend/public/data.json`.
2.  **Frontend**:
    ```bash
    cd frontend
    npm install
    npm run dev
    ```
3.  **AI Usage**: Enter your Gemini API Key in the header input and click "AI Categorize".
